description:
People are going missing on the streets of Hammerhal Aqsha – can the legendary witch hunters Callis and Toll get to the bottom of the mystery? Find out in this free Warhammer Age of Sigmar-themed episode of Hammer and Bolter.

Watch more action-packed animations at https://www.warhammertv.com.
